---
import Layout from "../../src/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Local Leader Designs">
  <main class="flex min-h-screen items-center justify-center bg-gray-50 px-4 py-10 sm:p-6">
    <div class="w-full max-w-5xl rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 text-center shadow-xl sm:p-8">
      <h1 class="mb-2 text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Local Leader Designs</h1>
      <p class="mb-8 text-gray-600">Six live landing page versions, each with its own design direction.</p>

      <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3">
        <a href="/v1" class="block p-6 rounded-xl border-2 border-gray-100 hover:border-primary hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200 group">
          <div class="mb-3 inline-flex rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-emerald-700">Live</div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 group-hover:text-primary mb-2">Version 1</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Original shared-layout landing page with the current premium SaaS refresh.</p>
        </a>

        <a href="/v1a" class="block p-6 rounded-xl border-2 border-gray-100 hover:border-primary hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200 group">
          <div class="mb-3 inline-flex rounded-full bg-blue-50 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-700">New Variant</div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 group-hover:text-primary mb-2">Version 1A</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">A tuned spin-off of v1 with a larger floating proof image, more Google-like reviews, refined pillar cards, and updated pricing polish.</p>
        </a>

        <a href="/v2" class="block p-6 rounded-xl border-2 border-gray-100 hover:border-primary hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200 group">
          <div class="mb-3 inline-flex rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-emerald-700">Live</div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 group-hover:text-primary mb-2">Version 2</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Renamed from the previous v3. Clean premium aesthetic with minimal cards and soft blur treatments.</p>
        </a>

        <a href="/v3" class="block p-6 rounded-xl border-2 border-gray-100 hover:border-primary hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200 group">
          <div class="mb-3 inline-flex rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-emerald-700">Live</div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 group-hover:text-primary mb-2">Version 3</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Premium minimal aesthetic with transparent proof-stack hero, visible texture, and two-offer pricing.</p>
        </a>

        <a href="/v4" class="block p-6 rounded-xl border-2 border-gray-100 hover:border-primary hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200 group">
          <div class="mb-3 inline-flex rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-emerald-700">Live</div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 group-hover:text-primary mb-2">Version 4</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Premium product-like aesthetic with transparent proof-stack hero, visible texture, and two-offer pricing.</p>
        </a>

        <a href="/v5" class="block p-6 rounded-xl border-2 border-gray-100 hover:border-primary hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200 group">
          <div class="mb-3 inline-flex rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-emerald-700">Live</div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 group-hover:text-primary mb-2">Version 5</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Premium warm aesthetic with transparent proof-stack hero, visible texture, and two-offer pricing.</p>
        </a>

        <a href="/v10" class="block p-6 rounded-xl border-2 border-gray-100 hover:border-primary hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200 group">
          <div class="mb-3 inline-flex rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-emerald-700">Live</div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 group-hover:text-primary mb-2">Version 10 (Demo)</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">A demonstration build showing what the v3/v4/v5 plans produce in practice.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
